{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1395938, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 274054, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "社会舆论太可怕了", "timestamp": 1617628423, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1395956, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 274054, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "哦", "timestamp": 1617628698, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1395964, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 274054, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "相关人没有精力做这个事情。", "timestamp": 1617628813, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1395982, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 274054, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "学校的名声比其他都重要", "timestamp": 1617628966, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1396021, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 274054, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我是真的不明白为什么非要学校公开，这件事和你有任何关系吗？除了满足你的好奇心？", "timestamp": 1617629368, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1396037, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 274054, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你自己想知道就通过你自己的渠道去打听。其他人哪来的义务去告诉你？", "timestamp": 1617629535, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1396061, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 274054, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "要做的是让学校加强防患于未然，这自然有推手在去做。自己吃人血馒头不要太有道理好吧。", "timestamp": 1617629755, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1396403, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 274054, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "学术研究表明公开自杀事件反而会造成更多的自杀", "timestamp": 1617633358, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1398489, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 274054, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 笑了，您至少给个ref吧，就这", "timestamp": 1617682425, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1398748, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 274054, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 谁在做？", "timestamp": 1617685862, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1401890, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 274054, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 怎么就人血馒头了，校内同学大多只是想关心一下同学，又不是垃圾营销号", "timestamp": 1617713821, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402003, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 274054, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Kate: 我倒是很想知道你怎么关心一个逝去的同学——不会是用“闲话”吧😅", "timestamp": 1617714600, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402395, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 274054, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果死者自己有遗书希望公开，可以朋友圈微博之类的发布，而不是要学校跟你公开。", "timestamp": 1617717046, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1402833, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 274054, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 这是确实，很多时候恶性事件都不会报道的", "timestamp": 1617720648, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1407326, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 274054, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: ？", "timestamp": 1617784836, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1407342, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 274054, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 也就你这种人会说闲话罢，为去世的同学感到惋惜都不行了？", "timestamp": 1617784938, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1409647, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 274054, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "人家想要且需要你的惋惜？人都走了就放过人家吧😅", "timestamp": 1617804688, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 17, "pid": 274054, "reply": 17, "tag": "令人不适", "text": "真的不懂，为啥一个个都搞的跟谜语人似的？有同学自杀了，都藏着掖着，连个屁都不敢放一声。直接面对这个事实有这么难吗？这种事情发生，所有人都不好受，所以不更应该让大家都知道这个事情，互相帮助，互相关心吗？不更应该提高各方面对这种事情的关注度，特别是学校的辣鸡的心理咨询服务，避免这种悲剧再次发生吗？不更应该去了解清楚原因，去做到防患于未然吗？", "timestamp": 1617628290, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1617804690, "url": "", "vote": {}}}